Package graph

Interface Graph<N extends Node<N,​E>,​E extends Edge<N,​E>>

  • Type Parameters:
    N - the type of nodes in this graph
    E - the type of edges in this graph
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdjacencyListGraph
    public interface Graph<N extends Node<N,​E>,​E extends Edge<N,​E>>
    A simple but flexible directed graph interface. The interface is generic in the Node and Edge types (N and E); concrete implementations will typically provide their own Node and Edge implementations and then use those types as the parameters N and E.
